{"tid":912304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"丹麥人會不會後悔？","createTime":"2018-11-22T14:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T17:37:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"805dc2ecad78439db6421d16a870bd4a8df81b8d","tid":912304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20181122/20551465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F20551465&d=E71%2FqmRBXvWyIIYlxP9zSl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0e799381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F20551465&h=4ee5d79b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20181122/20551465</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月22日 <br />\n<br />\n丹麥人會不會後悔？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181122/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181122%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=83461f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n去年四月開始，丹麥駐華使館向中國人大力推廣「丹麥蠔遊」活動，熱情邀請中國遊客去丹麥食蠔。為了讓中國人順利找到蠔源，使館網站圖文並茂列出詳細交通指引，又拍片介紹蠔的各種吃法。多管齊下，中國網民果然一窩蜂衝去丹麥食蠔，中國胃之威力，令丹麥人高興之餘亦震撼不已。<br />\n<br />\n丹麥人打開國門邀請中國人食蠔，當然是有原因的。原來丹麥海岸被太平洋生蠔入侵，早就蠔滿為患，保守估計那些蠔超過3,300噸，而當地人食慣歐洲本土野生蠔，對這種「次貨蠔」根本不屑一顧。丹麥政府擔心太平洋蠔喧賓奪主，破壞海洋生態，最終威脅本土Limfjord蠔的生存。所以想出這樣一個奇招。<br />\n<br />\n丹麥人不屑吃的太平洋蠔，對吃慣元素周期表的中國人來說，依然是天下美食，至少無污染，吃得放心。一眾花生友不擔心中國人的食力，擔心的是丹麥政府解決眼前困境後，會不會引狼入室，最終悔不當初。<br />\n<br />\n生蠔泛濫，丹麥政府放眼世界，眼光徐徐從不同膚色、種族、國家的人身上掠過，最後落在中國人身上，從這一點來說，對哲學素有研究的北歐人，對中國人的人性是有相當認知的。花生友大約不需要太替丹麥政府操心。<br />\n<br />\n其實，丹麥人也可以考慮開發生蠔出口產業，大批量傾銷到中國，這樣，沒有能力飛到北歐的中國人也能吃到太平洋蠔，滅蠔速度會快更多。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n是咁的法官大人誰煽惑佔中 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n男人之罪 (古德明)"},{"pid":"8efda3de8a853812ebe3f1da40cfb1abdbc91d26","tid":912304,"uid":200588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5cc18b8530305fdb53000fab1667aa62c51a6b","tid":912304,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"咁搵咩食中國人"},{"pid":"ec38ab0f545a85b4c026c3a656899eac69190b19","tid":912304,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5cc18b8530305fdb53000fab1667aa62c51a6b","tid":912304,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"咁搵咩食中國人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"毛澤東<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c2d303d9f5fd850eb686e0842e5c2dec37ad17","tid":912304,"uid":16927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"對吃慣元素周期表的中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}